## 📖 How Skills Work

**Structure:**
```
.claude/skills/
└── skill-name/
    └── SKILL.md          # Skill definition (instructions for Claude)
    └── examples/ (optional)
    └── templates/ (optional)
```

**Invoking a Skill:**
Claude will automatically use skills when relevant context appears in the conversation. You can also explicitly request a skill:

```
Use the [skill-name] skill to [task]
```

**Creating New Skills:**
See Claude Code documentation: https://code.claude.com/docs/en/skills

